9
00:01:15,200 --> 00:01:18,064
Two months ago, he took her for a drive...

10
00:01:18,233 --> 00:01:20,097
with another boyfriend.

11
00:01:21,000 --> 00:01:23,296
They made her drink whiskey...

12
00:01:23,734 --> 00:01:27,632
and then they tried to take advantage of her.

13
00:01:28,133 --> 00:01:30,225
She resisted.

14
00:01:30,400 --> 00:01:31,593
She kept her honor.

15
00:01:31,699 --> 00:01:32,393
So they beat her like an animal.

16
00:01:32,500 --> 00:01:32,795
When I went to the hospital, her nose was broken...

17
00:01:32,899 --> 00:01:34,126
