21
00:02:01,766 --> 00:02:04,699
She was the light of my life.

22
00:02:06,101 --> 00:02:08,623
Beautiful girl.

23
00:02:11,600 --> 00:02:15,362
Now she will never be beautiful again.

24
00:02:21,167 --> 00:02:23,359
Sorry.

25
00:02:30,767 --> 00:02:35,426
I went to the police like a good American.

26
00:02:35,600 --> 00:02:38,259
These two boys were brought to trial.

27
00:02:39,200 --> 00:02:41,928
A judge sentence them to three years in prison...

28
00:02:42,101 --> 00:02:44,760
and suspend their sentence.

29
00:02:45,400 --> 00:02:47,958
Suspended sentence.

30
00:02:48,233 --> 00:02:50,893
They went free that very day.

31
00:02:52,734 --> 00:02:56,132
I stood in the courtroom like a fool.

32
00:02:56,433 --> 00:03:00,126
And those two bastard, they smiled at me.

33
00:03:00,834 --> 00:03:04,163
Then I said to my wife, For justice...

34
00:03:04,467 --> 00:03:07,729
we must go to don Corleone.

35
00:03:11,834 --> 00:03:16,164
Why did you go to the police?
Why didn't you come to me first?

36
00:03:16,333 --> 00:03:18,095
What do you want of me?

37
00:03:18,267 --> 00:03:22,427
Tell me anything, but do what I beg you to do.

38
00:03:22,633 --> 00:03:24,792
What is that?

39
00:03:48,767 --> 00:03:51,232
That I cannot do.

40
00:03:51,900 --> 00:03:53,957
I'll give you anything you ask.

41
00:03:56,734 --> 00:03:58,132
We've known each other many
years, but this is the first time...

42
00:03:59,534 --> 00:04:02,897
you ever came to me for counsel or for help.

43
00:04:03,334 --> 00:04:06,061
I can't remember the last time that you invited me...

44
00:04:06,233 --> 00:04:08,961
to your house for a cup of coffee...

45
00:04:09,601 --> 00:04:13,397
even though my wife is godmother to your only child.

46
00:04:13,568 --> 00:04:15,591
But let's be frank.

47
00:04:15,801 --> 00:04:18,289
You never wanted my friendship...

48
00:04:18,800 --> 00:04:22,493
and you were afraid to be in my debt.

49
00:04:22,667 --> 00:04:25,031
I didn't want to get into trouble.

50
00:04:25,868 --> 00:04:28,356
I understand.

51
00:04:28,834 --> 00:04:32,198
You found paradise in America.

52
00:04:34,167 --> 00:04:36,133
You had a good trade, made a good living.

53
00:04:36,368 --> 00:04:38,993
Police protected you, and there were courts of law.

54
00:04:39,234 --> 00:04:42,427
So you didn't need a friend like me.

55
00:04:43,368 --> 00:04:46,994
