58
00:04:54,334 --> 00:04:56,960
You don't offer friendship.

59
00:04:57,135 --> 00:05:00,066
You don't even think to call me Godfather.

60
00:05:00,634 --> 00:05:02,293
Instead, you come into my house...

61
00:05:02,534 --> 00:05:03,965
